Stand 14 cookies end-to-end around side of 8-inch springform pan. Chop remaining cookies; place evenly on bottom of pan. Set aside. Stir boiling water into gelatin in small bowl 2 to 3 minutes or until completely dissolved; cool slightly. Pour into blender container. Add cottage cheese; cover. Blend until smooth; pour over chopped cookies in pan. Refrigerate 1 hour or until set. Arrange fruit on top of cheesecake. Garnish with thawed COOL WHIP Whipped Topping.